(6, 66, 'Result türü ile Olası Hataların ele alınması', 'result-tuerue-ile-olas-hatalar-n-ele-al-nmas', '<p>Metodumuzun diğer bölümü:</p>\r\n<div style=\"color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #282c34; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #98c379;\">expect</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">(</span><span style=\"color: #e5c07b;\">\"Satır okunamadı!\"</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">);</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Bu kodu şu şekilde de yazabilirdik:</p>\r\n<div style=\"color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #282c34; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">io</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">::</span><span style=\"color: #98c379;\">stdin</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">()</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #98c379;\">read_line</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">(</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">&amp;mut</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">tahmin</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">)</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #98c379;\">expect</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">(</span><span style=\"color: #e5c07b;\">\"Satır okunamadı!\"</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">);</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Ancak, tek bir uzun satır okuması zor, bu yüzden parçalara bölmek en iyisi.</p>\r\n<p>Daha önce de bahsedildiği gibi, <code>read_line</code> kullanıcının girdiği herhangi bir şeyi one verdiğimiz \'string\'e ekler, aynı zamanda bir değer de döndürür bu durumda <code>io::Result</code> değeri. Rust\'ın standart kütüphanesinde <code>Result</code> adında bir çok türü var. Genel <code>Result</code> ve spesifik olanlar <code>io::Result</code>. <code>Result</code> türleri \'enumaration\' genel olarak \'enum\' dır. Enum\'lar sık sık <code>match</code> ile kullanılır, <code>match</code> enum varyantlarına bakar belirli varyantlar için belirli kodları çalıştırır.</p>\r\n<p><code>Result</code>\'ın varyantları <code>Ok</code> ve <code>Err</code>. <code>Ok</code> varyantı operasyonun başarılı olduğunu bildirir, ve <code>Ok</code>\'in içinde başarılı sonuçtan gelen değer bulunur. <code>Err</code> varyantı operasyonun başarısız olduğunu bildirir, ve <code>Err</code> operasyonun neden başarısız olduğuna dair bilgi içerir.</p>\r\n<p><code>Result</code> türünün değerleri, aynı diğer türlerin değerleri gibi, kendi metodlarına sahiptir. Örnek olarak <code>io::Result</code>\'un <code>expect</code> adında bir metodu vardır. Eğer <code>io::Result</code> bir <code>Err</code> ise, <code>expect</code> programın hata vermesine ve kendisine verdiğin hata mesajının gösterilmesine yol açar. Eğer <code>io::Result</code> bir <code>Ok</code> ise, <code>expect</code> <code>Ok</code> içerisindeki değeri alır ve değişkene atar.</p>\r\n<div style=\"color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #282c34; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">PS C:\\RustProjects\\sayi_tahmin_oyunu&gt; cargo build</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> warning: unused `Result` that must be used</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> --&gt; src\\main.rs:9:5</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> |</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> 9 | io::stdin().read_line(&amp;mut tahmin);</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> |</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> = note: `#[warn(unused_must_use)]` on by default</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> = note: this `Result` may be an `Err` variant, which should be handled</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> warning: `sayi_tahmin_oyunu` (bin \"sayi_tahmin_oyunu\") generated 1 warning</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> Finished dev [unoptimized + debuginfo] target(s) in 0.01s</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Rust bizi <code>read_line</code> metodundan dönen <code>Result</code> değerini kullanmadığımız için uyararak, programımızın muhtemel bir hatayı ele almadığını söylüyor.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2022-06-04 10:32:15', 209, '', '2022-06-04 10:32:15', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-06-04 10:32:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 10, '', '', 1, 5, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(7, 67, 'println! ile Değerleri yazdırma', 'println-ile-degerleri-yazd-rma', '<div style=\"color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #282c34; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #98c379;\">println!</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">(</span><span style=\"color: #e5c07b;\">\"Tahminin: {}\"</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">, </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">tahmin</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">);</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Bu satır kullanıcı girişini içeren \'string\'i ekrana yazdırır. <code>{}</code> süslü parantezler yer tutucudur. Süslü parantezleri kullanarak birden fazla değer yazdırabiliriz. Birden fazla değer yazdırmak için aşağıdaki gibi yaparız:</p>\r\n<div style=\"color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #282c34; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #56b6c2;\">let</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">x</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">5</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #56b6c2;\">let</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">y</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">10</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #98c379;\">println!</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">(</span><span style=\"color: #e5c07b;\">\"x: {} y:{}\"</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">, </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">x</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">, </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">y</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">);</span></div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 2, '2022-06-05 10:52:22', 209, '', '2022-06-05 10:53:25', 209, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-06-05 10:52:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 3, 9, '', '', 1, 4, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(8, 68, 'Birinci Kısmı Test etme', 'birinci-k-sm-test-etme', '<p><code>cargo run</code> komutu ile şu ana kadar yaptıklarımızı test edelim.</p>\r\n<div style=\"color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #282c34; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #56b6c2;\">PS</span> <span style=\"color: #61afef;\">C</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">:</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">RustProjects</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">sayi_tahmin_oyunu</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">&gt; </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">cargo</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">run</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">   </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Compiling</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">sayi_tahmin_oyunu</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">v0</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">1</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">0</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">C</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">:</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">RustProjects</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">sayi_tahmin_oyunu</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">)</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">    </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Finished</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">dev</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> [</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">unoptimized</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">+</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">debuginfo</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">] </span><span style=\"color: #98c379;\">target</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">(</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">s</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">) </span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">in</span> <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">1</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">69s</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">     </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Running</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\"> `</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">target</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">debug</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">sayi_tahmin_oyunu</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">exe`</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">Sayıyı </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">tahmin</span> <span style=\"color: #98c379;\">et!</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">Lütfen </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">tahmininizi</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">girin</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">1</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Tahminin</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">:</span> <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">1</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #56b6c2;\">PS</span> <span style=\"color: #61afef;\">C</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">:</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">RustProjects</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">sayi_tahmin_oyunu</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">&gt; </span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Bu yaptıklarımız ile oyunumuzun ilk kısmı tamam. Kullanıcıdan girdi alıp ekrana yazdırıyoruz.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2022-06-05 10:55:58', 209, '', '2022-06-05 10:55:58', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-06-05 10:55:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext