(9, 69, 'Gizli Numara Oluşturma', 'rastgele-say-olusturma', '<p>Sırada kullanıcının tahmin etmesi için gizli bir sayı üretmek var. Gizli sayı her seferinde farklı olmalıki oynanabilir bir oyun olsun. 1 - 100 arasında bir sayı üreticez ki tahmin etmesi çok zor olmasın. Rust\'ın standart kütüphanesinde rastgele bir sayı üretecek method yok. Ama Rust takımının yaptığı bir <code>rand</code> adında crate var. <code>rand</code> crate\'inin içerisindeki metodlar ile rastgele bir sayı üretebiliriz.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2022-06-05 11:00:24', 209, '', '2022-06-05 11:00:57', 209, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-06-05 11:00:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 3, 7, '', '', 1, 4, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(10, 70, 'Daha Fazla İşlevsellik Elde Etmek İçin Crate Kullanma', 'daha-fazla-i-slevsellik-elde-etmek-i-cin-crate-kullanma', '<p>Rust takımının hazırladığı <code>rand</code> crate\'ini kullanabilmemiz için. <code>cargo.toml</code> dosyamızda <code>[dependencies]</code> kısmının altına <code>rand = \"0.8.5\"</code> yazıp kaydetmeliyiz.</p>\r\n<p>Sonrasında <code>cargo build</code> komutu ile gerekli dosyaları indirebiliriz. İndirme işlemi sonrası <code>rand</code> crate\'i içerisindeki metodları kullanabiliriz.</p>\r\n<div style=\"color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #282c34; font-family: Consolas, \'Courier New\', monospace; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; white-space: pre;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #56b6c2;\">PS</span> <span style=\"color: #61afef;\">C</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">:</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">RustProjects</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">\\</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">sayi_tahmin_oyunu</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">&gt; </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">cargo</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">build</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">    </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Blocking</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">waiting</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">for</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">file</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">lock</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">on</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">package</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">cache</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">    </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Updating</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">crates</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">io </span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">index</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">    </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Blocking</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">waiting</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">for</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">file</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">lock</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">on</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">package</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">cache</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">    </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Blocking</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">waiting</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">for</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">file</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">lock</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">on</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">package</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">cache</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">    </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Blocking</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">waiting</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">for</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">file</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">lock</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">on</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">build</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">directory</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">   </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Compiling</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">cfg</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">-if</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">v1</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">0</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">0</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">   </span><span style=\"color: #61afef;\">Compiling</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">ppv</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">-</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">lite86</span> <span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">v0</span><span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">2</span><span style=\"color: #abb2bf;\">.</span><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">16</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #bbbbbb;\">   </span><span st